MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the CH6 and CH8 postcode areas of Flint and Holywell, affecting properties in a widespread area. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at 10:39 am. Our engineers have arrived on site to investigate and repair the fault. Our team will work to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible. We expect the power to be restored by 12:45 pm. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 11:33 am on 13th April, 2021.

MAIN_MESSAGE: This is a message for customers in the FK10 postcode area of Alloa.
